<h1>Help &amp; How-To</h1>

<h4>Getting Started</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Log in with your account; your role (Admin, Manager, Employee) controls what you can do.</li>
    <li>Use the top navigation to access Items, Requests, Reports, and Admin sections.</li>
</ul>

<h4>Stationery Items</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Browse items; availability shows <strong>Available</strong> (stock minus reserved) and <strong>Reserved</strong>.</li>
    <li>Admins can create, edit, or delete items and upload images.</li>
</ul>

<h4>Requests</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Create a request by selecting items and quantities within available stock.</li>
    <li>Status flow: Pending â†’ Approved/Rejected. Employees can Withdraw while Pending.</li>
    <li>For approved requests, employees can Request Cancel; superiors/manager/admin can Approve Cancel. Employees can Withdraw Cancel while it is pending.</li>
    <li>Approvals deduct stock; cancellation approvals restore stock.</li>
</ul>

<h4>Eligibility / Budget</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Employees can view monthly budget limits based on their role and see spent/pending amounts.</li>
</ul>

<h4>Admin &amp; Manager</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Approve/Reject requests from the Requests list.</li>
    <li>Manage categories, roles, and (for Admin) users as needed.</li>
</ul>

<h4>Need Help?</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Contact your Admin if you cannot see expected options or need role changes.</li>
    <li>Report issues with stock or approvals to your Manager/Admin.</li>
</ul>

